Start your career and make something meaningful every day.
If you’re looking for opportunities to join the most creative, innovative and effcient workforce
in the entertainment industry’s most dynamic sector, then you should be looking at Take-Two!
JOIN US

OUR OFFICE
THE BENEFITS
PERKS & ACTIVITIES
INTERNSHIPS
JOIN US




LIFE AT TAKE-TWO
Headquartered in New York City, Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. is a leading developer, publisher and marketer of interactive entertainment for consumers around the globe. The Company develops and publishes products through its two wholly-owned labels Rockstar Games and 2K. Our products are designed for console systems and personal computers, including smartphones and tablets, and are delivered through physical retail, digital download, online platforms and cloud streaming services.
                    Why work for Take-Two?
Interactive entertainment is the strongest growing sector of the entertainment industry and Take-Two is at the forefront, producing some of the best-selling and highest-rated titles in the industry. Our world-class creative teams have developed 4 of the top 10 highest-rated titles for Xbox 360 and PS3 and more than 40 of our titles have sold multi-million units.
What does Take-Two have to offer?
At Take-Two, we foster success and productivity by maintaining a casual and inviting work environment, committing to individual and team development opportunities, providing comprehensive and leading-edge employee benefits and facilitating team-building activities in and out of the office.



Casual Dress Code
We want you to be comfortable while you work and we want you to be uniquely you. Our casual dress code allows employees to focus on their work while allowing the freedom to express one’s individual style.





Trendy New York SoHo Office
From the trendiest stores to the top restaurants and bars, and a vast selection of gyms, shopping and public transportation, Take-Two’s office is centrally located near all that New York City has to offer.





Fun Work Atmosphere
Even when we’re working hard, we like to have fun. We believe that when you enjoy coming to work and like the people with whom you work, you’ll be more efficient, innovate, productive and collaborative. 





Benefits, Perks & Activities
From comprehensive and leading-edge benefit plans to employee discounts to Company sponsored events and more, Take-Two believes in keeping our employees happy, healthy and engaged.






THE BENEFITS
Take-Two strives to offer a well-rounded and generous benefits program designed to provide you with coverage options with the flexibility to meet both individual and family needs.









Dental
We love to see our employees smile. Under Take-Two’s Delta Dental PPO Plan, preventative and diagnostic care is free and employees receive great savings on dental services from in-network providers.







Competitive Cigna Medical Plans
Take-Two’s Cigna plans offer high-quality, affordable medical coverage for you and your family, including doctors’ visits, hospitalization and emergency care.







Vision
Through Take-Two’s VSP Vision Benefits, we’ll keep your eyes seeing clearly with coverage that includes preventative care, as well as eye glasses and contact lenses.







Pre-Tax Commuter Benefits
Take-Two offers Pre-Tax Commuter Benefits that enable you to pay for qualified commuting expenses – public transportation, parking, ferry – without paying taxes on that money.







Additional Benefits
Different employees have different needs. We provide a variety of optional benefits, including Legal, Property and Pet Insurance. 







401K
We value the importance of saving for retirement. All employees are eligible for Take-Two’s Wells Fargo Retirement Plan with a Company matching of 50% on the first 6% you contribute.







Health & Dependent Care Flex Spending
It’s important to plan ahead. Take-Two’s Flex Spending Accounts allow you to set aside pre-tax dollars for your health and dependent care expenses.







Wellness Discounts
Preventative care is key in maintaining good health. We encourage all our employees to get their annual physical and offer a 5% discount on your medical premiums when you do.







Life Insurance & Disability Benefits
Take-Two provides Basic Life Insurance at no cost to you and our disability plans are designed to help protect your financial security in the event you are ever disabled.







PERKS & ACTIVITIES
At Take-Two, we value work-life balance and fun as much as hard work and encourage our employees to engage in activities in and out of the office with our many employee perks.






Employee Discount Program
Take-Two offers exclusive employee discounts on our games and merchandise and negotiates discounts with other vendors on products, fitness, tickets and more. 




Fitness Reimbursement Program
Take-Two encourages our employees to engage in regular physical activity and will reimburse you for your fitness expenses.




Employee Referral Bonus Program
Take-Two rewards our employees for referring qualified candidates who are subsequently hired as full-time regular employees.




Paid Time Off
Take-Two offers ample and flexible PTO so you can choose how to manage your days off.




Weekly Fruity Tuesdays
You can look forward to enjoying all the fresh fruit you can eat every Tuesday.




Snacks and Treats
Take-Two likes to reward our employees’ hard work with a treat (or two) with snacks, fresh fruit, bagels, ice cream, gourment coffee and more.




Sports and Event Ticket Raffles
Take-Two periodically receives tickets to some of the hottest sports and other events throughout the year which we raffle off to our employees. 




Events
Take- Two has many events throughout the year like our Winter Holiday Party, Summer Rooftop Party, Thanksgiving Potluck, JP MorganCorporate Challenge and more!







SUMMER INTERNSHIP PROGRAM

Take-Two’s Summer Internship Program is designed to provide students with an opportunity to gain substantive, first-hand business insight while building upon professional skills. Interns will gain hands-on exposure in the area(s) of their desired interests as well as participate in team-based summer-long projects.



3 Month Intensive Educational Enrichment Program
Internships available in most corporate departments
Regularly-scheduled seminars as part of a company-wide orientation




Intern events offer an opportunity to connect with department heads and supervisors, as well as your fellow Interns
Executive luncheons offer an exclusive opportunity to meet with Take-Two’s Executive Chairman/CEO, President and CFO.


INTERNSHIP OPPORTUNITIES




JOIN US
Come explore the endless opportunities in an environment where we support your professional success and growth. Take-Two is after talented individuals with original ideas and the passion to pursue them.
ALL AVAILABLE POSITIONS



Finance
The Finance Department oversees all financial aspects of Take-Two, including supporting our creative Labels and the international business with the month-end close, budgeting and forecasting, SEC filings, tax strategy and cash and debt management. The Department consists of the Corporate Controller’s group, Financial Reporting, Tax, Treasury, Financial Planning & Analysis, Accounts Payable and Accounts Receivable. 


Human Resources
The Human Resources Department serves as a strategic business partner to Take-Two’s leadership team to assist with attracting, retaining and developing employees. The HR team also executes effective policies and procedures to ensure that Take-Two’s values and mission are fulfilled.


IT
The Global IT Department drives IT strategy, development, and operations across the Take-Two enterprise.  Primary components include Applications, Infrastructure, and Online Engineering, which are further supported by pan-IT functions, including a PMO, Security, and Emerging IT.


Sales & Marketing
The Sales & Marketing Department is responsible for selling and channel marketing Take-Two’s video games to retail and distribution customers in the US, Canada & LATAM.  The Department handles global digital sales and customer marketing as well as provides sales planning and analysis for our customers and Take-Two Corporate.


Legal
The Legal Department provides advice to Take-Two and its affiliates and subsidiaries regarding all day-to-day legal matters. The Department serves the needs of the Company on a global basis, through attorneys, paralegals, and support staff located in the United States, the United Kingdom, and Asia.


Internal Audit
The Internal Audit Department assesses Take-Two’s internal control structure, advises management on developing control solutions, and monitors the implementation of these measures. The Department evaluates the effectiveness of the various business processes established by management with the purpose of identifying, assessing, managing, and monitoring the various financial and operational risks arising from the Company’s day-to-day activities.


Management & Corporate Development
The Management & Corporate Development team has oversight with respect to various facets of the corporate portfolio, growth and strategy.


Double Take (Comic Division)
The Double Take division is developing exciting new comic book and graphic novel products.


Product Development
Our Labels are hiring too! Check out career opportunities at 2K Games and Rockstar Games . 



